The recommended Perl module is:

  https://github.com/schwern/gravatar-url


Testing
--------

Clone the module under ~/devel/remote/gravatar_url:

  cd ~/devel/remote/
  git clone git://github.com/schwern/gravatar-url.git

Then put the test CGI under /var/www and create these symlinks:

  ln -s ~/devel/remote/gravatar_url/lib/Gravatar /var/www/
  ln -s ~/devel/remote/gravatar_url/lib/Libravatar /var/www/
